{"word":"H4608 - מַעֲלֶה - maʻăleh - mah-al-eh' - Ascent","slug":"H4608","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מַעֲלֶה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>maʻăleh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mah-al-eh'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Ascent"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05E2;&#x05DC;&#x05D4; - ma&#x201B;a&#x0306;leh</b> - <i>mah-al-eh'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H5927\">H5927</a>; an <i>elevation</i>, that is, (concretely) <i>acclivity</i> or <i>platform</i>; abstractly (the relation or state) a <i>rise</i> or (figuratively) <i>priority: - </i>ascent, before, chiefest, cliff, that goeth up, going up, hill, mounting up, stairs."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H131\">H131</a>, <a href=\"#/H4605\">H4605</a>, <a href=\"#/H4607\">H4607</a>, <a href=\"#/H4609\">H4609</a>, <a href=\"#/H4610\">H4610</a>, <a href=\"#/H5920\">H5920</a>, <a href=\"#/H5921\">H5921</a>, <a href=\"#/H5927\">H5927</a>, <a href=\"#/H5929\">H5929</a>, <a href=\"#/H5930\">H5930</a>, <a href=\"#/H5933\">H5933</a>, <a href=\"#/H5935\">H5935</a>, <a href=\"#/H5940\">H5940</a>, <a href=\"#/H5941\">H5941</a>, <a href=\"#/H5942\">H5942</a>, <a href=\"#/H5944\">H5944</a>, <a href=\"#/H5945\">H5945</a>, <a href=\"#/H8585\">H8585</a>"}]}